description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Moving Better for Father's Day' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Comfort Moves vibe means Safe, cozy, feel-good movement. This is especially good for Those who want to move but need it to feel easy and accessible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Move through everyday mobility exercises with Peter in this workout dedicated to all the dads and role models.
